<div class="com-share" data-id="2866" data-title="《如果转投索尼，Adele 还会是那个酷酷的胖女孩吗？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/2866/medium/2866.jpg?1436655121" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/2866" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
